## Notes

- Both surfaces use inline CSS injection (no external stylesheet changes) to maintain csTimer compatibility
- All data loading is async with graceful fallback for empty state
- Goal card selection state is tracked but plan-setup flow is not yet wired (per task scope)
- The "Stats" tab on entry home navigates to the weakness summary surface
- Category tab switching on weakness summary re-renders the ranking table dynamically
